    • Field Detail

      • formula

        private String formula
        Formula of the group to be counting. May be a ChemAxon-defined shortcut group, or may be a SMILES representation with the 1st atom counting as the attachment point.

      • number

        private int number
        Number of groups to compare against.

      • orientation

        private int orientation
        Whether to count axial or equatorial groups.

      • overrideForIndeterminate

        private transient boolean overrideForIndeterminate
        Whether to override the author's feedback when ACE cannot determine whether a group is axial or equatorial.
